description: I´m in Tuscany on vacation. So once again, my deputy is in charge of our operations back in Prague. The poor boy must endure that horrible rainy weather while I lie on the beach and drink vine all day. I wasn´t surprised when he told me that he had a little fun yesterday. I couldn´t blame him, the work is sometimes a bit dull and we all need some distraction. To me, this guy looked impossible to get, but my deputy surprised me. He gave him the proper treatment our agency is famous for. Maybe being too subtle isn´t always the best way to go. This guy ended so fucked up, he didn´t even read though the contract, he just signed it and left. He didn´t even sit down. Maybe he couldn´t. His ass was a proper virgin hole before he decided to use to forward his career.
title: Dirty Scout 52
